Privacy Policy for Elowen

1. Introduction

Welcome to the privacy policy for Elowen. We are dedicated to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring the protection of your personal data. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and secure your information when you interact with our bot on Discord.

2. Information We Collect

Our bot may collect the following types of information:

Discord User Information: Includes your username, user ID, and any messages you send to the bot. This data is collected to facilitate the bot's functionalities, such as responding to commands and providing personalized interactions.
Interaction Data: Details on how you use the bot, including commands issued and interactions. This data helps us enhance the botâ€™s performance and user experience.

3. Use of Information

The collected information is utilized for the following purposes:

Service Provision and Enhancement: To respond to your commands and tailor the bot's interactions to improve your experience.
Security Measures: To monitor and ensure that the bot is used in compliance with our terms of service and to prevent misuse.
Communication: To inform you of updates or resolve any issues related to the bot.

4. Information Sharing

We do not disclose your personal information to third parties, except in the following circumstances:

Legal Compliance: When required by law or to protect our legal rights or the safety of our users.
Service Providers: With third-party service providers who assist in operating and maintaining the bot, solely to the extent necessary for those functions and in compliance with this privacy policy.

5. Data Security

We employ robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Despite these measures, no data transmission over the internet can be guaranteed as completely secure.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to access, correct, or request the deletion of your personal information. To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided below.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Significant changes will be communicated to you, and the revised policy will be made available for review.

8. Contact Information

For any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy or the handling of your information, please contact us at:

Email: elowenbot@outlook.com
